  <para>
    <classname>ICPreconditioner</classname> is a <xref
    linkend="RegisteredClass-Preconditioner"/> that uses Incomplete
    Cholesky factorization to speed up the convergence of an iterative <link
    linkend="RegisteredClass-MatrixMethod">matrix method</link>.  It
    is applicable only to symmetric positive definite matrices.
  </para>
  <para>
    &oof2;'s <classname>ICPreconditioner</classname> uses the
    <classname>ICPreconditioner</classname> from <ulink
    url="http://math.nist.gov/sparselib++/">SparseLink++</ulink>.
  </para>



